ed="T" n="0882a20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0882a20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>雅州開元寺<persName key="A013762">智廣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0882a21"/><persName key="A013762">釋智廣</persName>，姓崔氏，不知何許人也。德瓶素完，<lb
ed="T" n="0882a22"/>道根惟固，化行<placeName key="PL000000036649">洪雅</placeName>，特顯奇蹤。凡百病者造<lb
ed="T" n="0882a23"/>之，則以片竹為杖，指其痛端，或一撲之，無<lb
ed="T" n="0882a24"/>不立愈。至有𤼣者則起，跛者則奔，其他小<lb
ed="T" n="0882a25"/>疾，何足言哉。<date notBefore-iso="+0894-02-14" key="j20476322048051" notAfter-iso="+0895-04-09"><anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz5"/>乾<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz5"/>寧初</date>，<ref type="person" target="#A006588">王氏</ref>始定<placeName key="PL000000034805">成都</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000037025">雅郡</placeName>守<lb
ed="T" n="0882a26"/>羅（亡名）罷任，携<persName key="A013762">廣</persName>來謁。<placeName key="PL000000034649">蜀</placeName>主<ref type="person" target="#A006588">王氏</ref>素知奇術，<lb
ed="T" n="0882a27"/>唯呼為聖師焉。先是<date notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21" key="j20355242040636" notAfter-iso="+0874-12-20">咸通中</date><ref type="person" target="#A013746">南蠻王</ref>及<ref type="person" target="#A019501">坦綽</ref><ptr target="#n2044"/><lb
ed="T" n="0882a28"/>來圍<placeName key="PL000000034805">成都</placeName><ptr target="#n2045"/>，<placeName key="PL000000034805">府</placeName>幾陷。時天王現沙門形，高五<lb
ed="T" n="0882a29"/>丈許，眼射流光，蠻兵即退。故<placeName key="PL000000034649">蜀</placeName>人於城北<pb ed="T" n="0882b" xml:id="T50.2061.0882b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0882b01"/><placeName key="PL000000034759">寶曆寺</placeName>立五丈僧相。後為<persName key="A013763">牛尚書</persName>預毀。次<lb
ed="T" n="0882b02"/>兵火相仍，唯懼毘沙<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz7"/>門<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz7"/>之頹<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>𡉏</sic><corr>圮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz9"/>耳。<ref type="person" target="#A006588">王氏</ref>乃語<lb
ed="T" n="0882b03"/><persName key="A013762">廣</persName>曰：「<anchor xml:id="beg0882004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>郎</sic><corr>師</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0882004"/>之異術，道德動人，乘此可料理<lb
ed="T" n="0882b04"/>天王否？往<persName key="A019502">吳尚書行魯</persName>曾夢令修吾像，方<lb
ed="T" n="0882b05"/>事經營，除書忽到。請法力成之。」<persName key="A013762">廣</persName>唯其命，<lb
ed="T" n="0882b06"/>徙就天王閣<!--找不到此地-->下，居一隅，小榻而已。翌日，病者<lb
ed="T" n="0882b07"/>填噎其門，日收所施二十萬至三十萬錢。<lb
ed="T" n="0882b08"/>又發言勸人出材木，浹旬皆運至，堆<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz11"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>積</sic><corr>𧂐</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz11"/>，令<lb
ed="T" n="0882b09"/>三綱掌管焉。初<persName key="A013762">廣</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000037025">雅郡</placeName>本寺羯帝神堂內，<lb
ed="T" n="0882b10"/>居其半室，低門苫蓐，不許女人到門。唯有<lb
ed="T" n="0882b11"/>一竹箜子。每齋，受嚫二十文，必投箜內，滿<lb
ed="T" n="0882b12"/>則置之佛殿。聲鐘集眾，自他平等<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz13"/>分<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz13"/>之。常<lb
ed="T" n="0882b13"/>日俗家請齋，亦體<persName key="A013762">廣</persName>意，<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz15"/>止<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz15"/>施二十文，淨飯<lb
ed="T" n="0882b14"/>菜豉汁，此外不許一物，嚫多不取，食畢而<lb
ed="T" n="0882b15"/>去，亦無辭告。其後益加神驗，或遇病者，一<lb
ed="T" n="0882b16"/>摑一叱皆起。或令燒紙緡，掇散飲食。或遇<lb
ed="T" n="0882b17"/>甚痛惱者，捩紙蘸水，貼之亦差。<date from-iso="+0898-09-20" key="j20493112049461" to-iso="+0899-02-17">光化元年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0882b18"/>修天王閣<!--找不到此地-->，向畢，乃循江瀆池，呪食飼魚。經<lb
ed="T" n="0882b19"/>夜，其魚二尺已上。萬億許皆浮水面而殞。<lb
ed="T" n="0882b20"/>聊躡流水，救十千魚生忉利同也。</p>
